snippet.title: GAMEPLAY TRAILER | NEW GAME BASED ON THE OUTCAST
snippet.description:
The official video game adaptation of the highly-regarded mythical martial arts franchise The Outcast will launch on mobile devices! The debut trailer showcases the distinct art style, exhilarating fight animations, kinetic combat system, and captivating Inhuman World players can explore.

#TheOutcast
